column1: This table is field data collected in the Caribou Creek Watershed in the Caribou Poker Creek Research Watershed North of Fairbanks
This data set was created by George Allen and Dr David Butman by pacing along streams and taking wetted stream width measurements every 5 meters with a tape measure
This data was collected to determine the distribution of stream widths in headwater catchments.
